Freestyle Project
New Item   →   Name: Maven-CI   →   Select: Freestyle Project   →   OK

Source Code Management   →   Git   →   Add repo URL  (e.g., https://github.com/...)

Build Step   →   Add   →   Invoke top-level Maven targets   →   Goals: clean package

Post-build Action   →   Add   →   Publish JUnit test result report   →   Path: **/target/surefire-reports/*.xml

Save   →   Click Build Now   → Check Console Output   →   Look for BUILD SUCCESS




